---
import noahImg from "../assets/img/noah.webp";
---

<section
	class="relative isolate overflow-hidden px-6 py-20 text-white sm:px-10 md:py-32"
>
	<div
		class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-70"
		aria-hidden="true"
	>
		<div
			class="absolute left-1/4 top-12 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[#ff7a00]"
		></div>
		<div
			class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[#ff7a00]"
		></div>
		<div
			class="absolute right-20 top-1/3 h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[#ff7a00]"
		></div>
		<div
			class="absolute -left-12 top-1/2 h-48 w-48 rounded-full bg-[#ff7a00]/10 blur-3xl"
		></div>
		<div
			class="absolute right-0 top-0 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-[#ff7a00]/5 blur-[120px]"
		></div>
	</div>

	<div
		class="relative z-10 mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10 text-center md:flex-row md:items-center md:text-left"
	>
		<div class="relative mx-auto w-48 shrink-0 sm:w-56 md:mx-0 md:w-64 lg:w-72">
			<div
				class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 rounded-full bg-[#ff7a00]/30 blur-3xl"
				aria-hidden="true"
			></div>
			<div
				class="rounded-full border border-[#ff7a00]/40 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0f0f0f] to-[#1f1f1f] p-2 shadow-[0_0_35px_rgba(255,122,0,0.4)]"
			>
				<img
					src={noahImg.src}
					width={noahImg.width}
					height={noahImg.height}
					alt="Portrait de Noah Rognon"
					loading="lazy"
					class="aspect-square w-full rounded-full border-4 border-[#ff7a00]/40 object-cover shadow-[0_0_45px_rgba(255,122,0,0.45)]"
				/>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="w-full max-w-2xl space-y-8 text-center md:w-auto md:max-w-xl md:text-left">
			<div class="space-y-3">
				<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-white md:text-5xl">
					&Agrave; propos de moi
				</h1>
				<p class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#ff7a00]">
					D&eacute;veloppeur web et &eacute;tudiant en BUT MMI
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-200 md:text-lg">
				<p>
					Je m&apos;appelle Noah Rognon, &eacute;tudiant en 2e ann&eacute;e de BUT MMI &agrave; Montb&eacute;liard,
					sp&eacute;cialis&eacute; en d&eacute;veloppement web et dispositifs interactifs (DWeb).
				</p>
				<p>
					Je con&ccedil;ois des sites et applications web complets, du front-end au back-end,
					avec une attention particuli&egrave;re port&eacute;e &agrave; l&apos;exp&eacute;rience utilisateur et &agrave; la qualit&eacute; du code.
				</p>
				<p>
					Polyvalent gr&acirc;ce &agrave; mon parcours m&ecirc;lant programmation, design et communication, je vise &agrave; devenir
					d&eacute;veloppeur web full stack, capable de cr&eacute;er des solutions modernes, performantes et accessibles.
				</p>
			</div>

			<div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#ff7a00]">
				<span class="inline-flex h-1 w-12 rounded-full bg-current"></span>
				<span class="inline-flex h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-current"></span>
				<span class="inline-flex h-1 w-12 rounded-full bg-current"></span>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
